UNITY OPTO TECH said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 5.35% to NT$587,025,000 from NT$620,193,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            587,025          620,193    
YOY%              -5.35%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,059,194        2,847,896   
YOY%             -27.69% 
=================================================================
 